Title: Fix KeyError for "Site ID" painter if site is missing
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: multisite
Date: 1651484316
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
State: unknown
Version: 2.2.0i1

If the painter "Site ID" is used in views were the site is missing, e.g. "All
aggregations", the error "KeyError: 'site'" occurred.
